\F[1]\AA[F]Rather than being locked... it feels like it's
being held down with incredible force...............
What have you been rummaging around for since earlier?

\F[1]\AA[F]There's no one here... I'm sure I heard a voice
though.
I'm right in front of you.

\F[17]\AA[F]No, no way....\c[14]The one sitting on that sofa
is....
\F[10]\AA[F](I heard a voice, but I want to ignore it)
\F[10]\AA[F]Let's start by searching this room, shall we?

\F[1]\AA[F]I wonder if this room is like this. I have to
tell Ann for now.

\F[17]\AA[F](Thanks to my mind being read, it's convenient
not having to go report in person.)

You're quick to understand and excellent, Miss Celia.
There's a reason why Lady Sadi likes you....

\F[1]\AA[F]Based on the original diary I saw, there are
still scattered pages left, right? I'll help you find them.

Wow! What a good-natured person... You're so wonderful it's
almost annoying.

Actually, it's beyond that \c[14]door\c[0]....
...........But before that.
I'll give a reward to the kind and good-natured Miss Celia.

\c[14]It's a code\c[0]. The second digit is \c[14]8\c[0].
Please remember it.

\F[6]\AA[F](An... Elixir from the shelf? What unexpected
luck! Helping others really does pay off!)
\F[6]\AA[F]Then I'll go to the room ahead. Wait for me!

\c[14]With the acquisition of the second digit of the code
'8'\c[0], it became possible to go to the room ahead.

\F[10]\AA[F]It seems to be well taken care of... but by
whom?
addLog　セリアは昔人形遊びしていた事を思い出している

\F[10]\AA[F]It seems to be well taken care of... but by
whom?

\F[1]\AA[F](Come to think of it, I've heard about this at
school)

\F[1]\AA[F](I heard there are ability users called
Necromancers who can freely manipulate inanimate objects...)
Um... I am who I am.
My name is An\c[14]Anthurium\c[0], Miss Celia.
I'd like you to call me An.
An knows because he's been watching you all this time.

\c[27]I just had a kiss, intertwining saliva with that
person.
\F[9]\AA[F]Ah, it's not like I enjoyed that!!
\c[27]That's a lie... It was so passionate♡

\F[17]\AA[F](What's with this doll... Come to think of it,
since a while ago...)

\F[17]\AA[F](I feel like even the things I haven't said out
loud are being understood...\c[0])
I'm envious that you can interact so closely with Lady Sadi.

\F[10]\AA[F]... Lady? So, you're really part of the Demon
King's army...!!
An has always been in the church....

\F[1]\AA[F]That's enough. Once I know you're an enemy,
you're useless to me! So, goodbye.
You want me to stay by your side?
\F[15]\AA[F](If I anger her, it might be dangerous...)
[The Hearts of Two] Changes in Celia
Isn't it? I want you to enjoy the tea party.
Ask about having your mind read
The questions are over, so let's move the conversation forward

\F[1]\AA[F]Hey, who exactly are you, Anthurium? You cut me
off earlier, but you said always at the church....

\F[15]\AA[F]Wait a minute. Are you sure you're not a
necromancer? I can't find the puppeteer controlling the
dolls, but...

Necro...? I don't know about that. An doesn't have a
physical body to begin with, \c[14] I'm currently using a
doll as a medium.

Originally, I came here from the spirit world and have long
been stored in the church, possessing a certain
weapon\c[14]\c[0]...
\F[1]\AA[F]You're a spirit...! And, you mentioned a weapon?
I've been told to keep it a secret by Lady Sadi♡

\F[10]\AA[F](If it's a weapon, I'm sure \c[14]Hayato can use
it...!\c[0])

\c[14]A man came to take the weapon a year ago...\c[0]
That's why An left the storage room.

So now I'm possessing a doll in this room... It's not too
bad.
心を読まれてる事について聞く

\F[10]\AA[F]Um, haven't you been responding even to things I
haven't said out loud?
As a spirit, An can easily read human thoughts.

\c[27]Resonance\c[0]... The ability to share emotions and
thoughts. This is just one of many abilities.
\F[10]\AA[F]Hmm... It's a mysterious ability, isn't it?

\F[10]\AA[F](But this might be my first time dealing with a
spirit... I wonder how Hayato is doing.)

\F[9]\AA[F]Can you stop doing that already!? I can't even
think!
I'll stop if you change the subject.
質問は済んだので会話を進める
\F[1]\AA[F](I've pretty much asked everything I wanted to.)

\F[10]\AA[F](An is a spirit that uses a doll as a medium,
and furthermore, she has the power to share thoughts...)

\F[3]\AA[F]I've been the only one asking questions, so I was
wondering if you had anything to ask.
................... \c[14]I want you to listen to my\c[0] troubles.

Aren't you going to laugh? 'A spirit without a physical body
falling in love' sounds ridiculous, doesn't it...

\F[1]\AA[F]Not at all. I think falling in love is a
beautiful thing.
\F[1]\AA[F](So even in the spirit world, there is love.)
...！　I had a slight misunderstanding about Miss Celia. But....
I know it's an unrequited love, so my heart is in pain.

\F[18]\AA[F]Unrequited, you say... Why are you worrying so
much! Why don't you try expressing your feelings with a go-
for-broke attitude!
\F[10]\AA[F](I don't have the power to set things up!)

\F[18]\AA[F]Who is the person you're in love with in the
first place!?

\F[10]\AA[F](Or rather, that guy...\c[27]Can he even charm
spirits?\c[0] What kind of person is he...!)
For Anthurium, it's a lofty aspiration....

\F[16]\AA[F]That's not the case. But are you sure?
\c[27]That guy... he may not look bad on the outside,
but....
It's a... rain of black tea.

\F[10]\AA[F](Or rather, that guy...\c[27]Can he even charm
spirits?\c[0] What kind of person is he...!)

\c[27]Of course, since Lady Celia is with Lord Sadi, I've
given up in my heart. \c[0]But I can't suppress my
feelings....

Anthurium has a diary where she writes about her feelings
for such a gentleman....
\c[14]It seems the pages have been scattered somewhere.
\c[14]Please\c[0]... won't you help me gather them?

\F[17]\AA[F]................. (\c[14]Is this what the sixth
request in the rulebook is referring to...?\c[0])
\F[17]\AA[F](That means he's in cahoots with Sadi.)

\F[36]\AA[F](Or perhaps...\c[14]he's exploiting\c[0] her
feelings of love)
`見た目は人形だけど、「恋」するなんて案外人間味あるのね。`

\F[17]\AA[F] (It's an unnatural story, but then again,
Anthurium is a supernatural phenomenon after all.)
\F[1]\AA[F]Um... I've brought a lot of torn pages.

\F[10]\AA[F](Even though she's a doll, it's clear that she's
feeling down. No wonder there was no response until now.)
I'm... I'm really sorry, Miss Celia.
I was so desperate to be liked by Lady Sadi, I lost control!

\F[16]\AA[F]I understand... I really do. So, let's let
bygones be bygones, okay?

\F[16]\AA[F]I understand that Anthurium was trying her best
to be useful to her... right, Anthurium?
Miss Celia... How noble you are...

\F[16]\AA[F]Don't worry about it, Anthurium. So, let's let
bygones be bygones, okay?
\F[1]\AA[F]I fled here from the war a year ago.

\F[6]\AA[F]I was attacked by monsters while escaping, and
bombs were flying around... Compared to that, this is
nothing!
\F[10]\AA[F](The armor... It was incredibly scary, but)

Miss Celia... I'm deeply moved that you're encouraging me
while hiding your own fear.

\F[1]\AA[F]...That's right, Anthurium. As a sign of
reconciliation, there's something I'd like to ask of you.
Please feel free to ask me anything.

\F\c[14]\AA[F]You said at the beginning, \c[14]I've been
watching you all for a long time\c[0], didn't you?

\F[10]\AA[F]...Can you see the current situation in the
prison? Like what Hayato and Merill are doing....

\c[27]They're not doing anything right now\c[0]. There's no
problem with their MP either.

\F[6]\AA[F]...I'm relieved. Since there was no response from
Hayato, I thought something serious had happened.
................I'm glad to see that you're pleased.

And, Miss Celia. There is something I want to tell you from
my side as well, at the end.
\F[6]\AA[F]Hehe, don't be so coy. Why don't you say it?

The first thing is, beyond the room from earlier, there's
the \c[14]final page\c[0].

Do you understand if I say it's near the place where the
armor was \c[14]\c[0]?

I will tell you the \c[14]password\c[0] to pass through
there. ...............
I'll say it one more time.

This is about the \c[14]weapon\c[0] that Anthurium has been
managing for a long time.

\c[14]The weapon storage room\c[0] is completely unaffected
by Lady Sadi's magic. It should be somewhere.

...If Miss Celia continues to move forward with her \c[27]noble
will\c[0], she may eventually reach that storage room.

I can't disclose the details of the weapon, but at least
this... The one who came to take Anthurium's weapon a year
ago was...
\c[14]The weapon is still stuck there, you know\c[0]
That's all I can tell you from Anthurium.

\F[15]\AA[F] (...What does that mean? The hero took that
weapon, right? But Hayato said his older brother died...)

\F[15]\AA[F](Does that mean someone returned it?
\c[14]During the ceasefire\c[0]?)

\F[15]\AA[F] (Even if it's the hero's weapon, it's
definitely powerful. Is there a need to confine it in the
storage room?)

I apologize for interrupting your thoughts... First, I would
like you to go and retrieve the last page of the diary.
